title: Watch how the iPhone 15 handles the bend test that busted the Pro Max
description: The YouTuber who recently busted the back of an iPhone 15 Pro Max in a durability test is back. And this time he's bending the iPhone 15.

title: NASA’s record-breaking astronaut arrives home safely
description: Frank Rubio has landed safely back on Earth after becoming the first NASA astronaut to spend a full year in space – six months longer than the original plan.

title: Meta pays big bucks to end office lease that still had 18 years left
description: The move is a sign of the times, with tech giants and other large companies responding to the popularity of remote working since the pandemic.
